XS轻量模型系列在库编号100+轻量模型将有新的工作流和使用方式，大致分为主体轻量模型与辅助轻量模型（LoRa、Loha、Perfusion、TI、VAE等）

主体轻量模型：XSArchi_1***V1，V1将作为主体轻量模型编号进行规整命名，在工作流中起到主导图像生成的工作，复合功能将决定于轻量模型功能。使用权重在0.5-1.3左右。

辅助轻量模型：XSArchi_1***V1.1，V1.1（即此Lora第二版）将作为辅助轻量模型编号进行规整命名，在工作流中起到辅助图像生成的工作，无复合功能，分为视角、风格、应用场景等20余种功能轻量模型，详细功能将在轻量模型介绍中标出。使用权重在0.1-0.5左右。

V2+轻量模型将被更新或迭代。

新轻量模型将分为两种不同的训练、融合、提取等方式进行制作，在库编号相同但版本不同的轻量模型，在训练集的处理上大致无异。在库编号不同但版本相同的轻量模型，功能不同外，训练集及训练方式也各不相同。

新版本将加入中英文命名的方式，解决大家对于模型标识、分类出现的困难。

其余版本介绍：

在库编号100-的轻量模型为早期试用模型，将被迭代。

在库编号100+的轻量模型为正式模型，分为商用及非商用模型，将会持续更新。

在库编号百位数以复数形式出现的为独立授权模型，针对不同平台、企业、组织、个人等进行授权、商用、非商用流通。

在库含有编号的轻量模型被认作为垂类模型库在库模型，将配合XS工作流进行使用。

XS Lightweight model series in the library number 100+ lightweight model will have a new workflow and use methods, roughly divided into the principal lightweight model and auxiliary lightweight model (LoRa, Loha, TI, VAE, etc.).

Body lightweight model: XSArchi_1***V1, V1 will be structured and named as the body lightweight model number, and play a leading role in image generation in workflow. Composite function will be determined by the function of the lightweight model. The right to use weight is around 0.5-1.3.

Auxiliary lightweight model: XSArchi_1***V1.1, V1.1 (i.e., the second version of Lora) will be structured and named as the auxiliary lightweight model number, and play an auxiliary role in image generation in workflow. There is no compound function, and it is divided into more than 20 functional lightweight models such as perspective, style and application scene. The right to use is about 0.1 to 0.5.

V2+ lightweight model will be updated or iterated.

The new lightweight model will be divided into two different ways of training, fusion, extraction and so on. The lightweight model with the same library number but different versions will be roughly the same in the processing of the training set. In addition to the different functions of lightweight models with different library numbers but the same version, the training sets and training methods are also different.

The new version will add the way of naming in Chinese and English to solve the difficulties of model identification and classification.

Introduction to other versions:

The lightweight model in library number 100- is an early trial model that will be iterated.

The lightweight models in the library number 100+ are official models, divided into commercial and non-commercial models, and will be updated continuously.

The number of hundreds in the database appears in the plural form as an independent authorization model, which carries out authorization, commercial and non-commercial circulation for different platforms, enterprises, organizations, individuals, etc.

The numbered lightweight models in the library are considered as vertical model models and will be used in conjunction with the XS workflow.

items.name: 【Character】Noir (NIKKE)
items.description:
Introduction

I originally planned to make this model when I have enough images of Noir, but I didn't expect the current results to be quite good, so I decided to release this model. This model can generate Noir from Goddess of Victory: NIKKE. The trigger tag is 'noir \(nikke\)'. The key features are 'dark-skinned female, playboy bunny, rabbit ears, black pantyhose, lace-trimmed legwear, black leotard, yellow eyes, brown hair, fishnets'. The 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) are recommended. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version (original) YesMix. Now you can generate masterpiece with Blanc.

Cautions (Must Read)

For anime model,

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

  • Some preview images are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled using 'SD Upscale'. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

BTW, make sure set this option in 'Stable Diffusion' settings to 'CPU' to successfully regenerate the preview images with the same seed.

  • The training resolution of this model is 1024x1024, so generating resolution must not exceed this range. Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.name: Robert Rauschenberg Style
items.description:
Robert Rauschenberg was an American artist known for his groundbreaking contributions to the art world and his influential role in the development of pop art and mixed-media techniques.

His style can be described as innovative, interdisciplinary, and characterized by the blending of various mediums and materials. Rauschenberg often incorporated everyday objects, such as found objects, photographs, fabrics, and newspapers, into his artworks, challenging the boundaries of traditional art forms.

He pioneered the use of collage and assemblage techniques, creating layered and visually dynamic compositions that combined painting, sculpture, and printmaking. Rauschenberg's artworks often incorporated elements of abstraction, bold colors, and bold brushwork.

One of his most famous works is "Erased de Kooning Drawing," in which he famously obtained a drawing from Willem de Kooning and erased it as an artistic gesture, questioning notions of authorship and the value of art.

Rauschenberg's art was not only visually striking but also carried social and political commentary. He explored themes of consumerism, mass media, and the intersection of art and life.

His collaborations with choreographers, musicians, and performers demonstrated his belief in the integration of art and the wider cultural sphere. Rauschenberg's openness to interdisciplinary practices and his willingness to challenge artistic conventions made him a highly influential figure in the art world.

Robert Rauschenberg's innovative approach and fearless experimentation continue to inspire contemporary artists. His contributions to the art world have left a lasting impact, reshaping the possibilities of artistic expression and expanding the definition of what constitutes art.

items.name: Gou - Hentai University
items.description:
This is a LoRA for the character Gou, from Hentai University a game by Noodle Jacuzzi.

Gou's art is from the artist Gujira, the sets -

Kimeseku ni Maketa Shounen & Succubus♂ o Zetsurin de Toriko ni suru!!

I've been working my way through making these for all the characters currently in the game, and sharing them in the Discord for HU, but figured I should also put them up here.

In general, I'm working from pretty limited image sets, so expect the results to be a bit wonky at times. Another one of the boys, so as always you've gotta work with what the AI gives you there.

I recommend a weight of around 0.5, possibly lower depending if you're combining the character LoRA with other styles/costumes/etc. along with tagging some defining characteristics of the character you're generating. Higher than that can really push the artist's original style, and may cause you issues.

All characters I train have a "character tag" added into the set to help generate them fairly reliably. Gou's got two different looks. The lora tends to default to human form, but a few tags and you can get his succubus form reliably.

Recommended LoRA Weight - 0.5 for fairly flexible, higher if you want more of the original artist's style, lower if it doesn't play nice with other loras.

Character tag - HUGou, 1boy, flat chest
Recommended tags - brown hair, short hair, purple eyes, / purple hair, dark skin, bat wings, low wings,

I've got quite a backlog of these made up already, so I'll be uploading them on and off.

Check my other uploads as I put them out for more HU characters, and if you want any specific character put up soon, let me know.

items.name: 永雏塔菲 · 3D偶像服
items.description:
我去，这不是我们《圆神》里的鹿目圆吗

是3D偶像服大菲喵。推荐 prompts：

yellow eyes, white skirt, white gloves, pink hair

可根据实际需求自行调整，一般来说并不需要写全 tags。

更新日志

v4.0 数据集优化——现在无需特意指定背景，并且人物特征更加明显。可以添加 flat_chest 避免可能的大奶子出图。

v3.0 数据集优化，现在生成的图片应该更高清了

v2.0 采用 LoRA 方法炼图（不是 LoHa），推荐指定背景和人物视角。如果出现大头照，建议使用 cowboy shot、full body、upper body 等 tags 规避。

推荐阅读

https://civitai.com/models/69411/guide-how-to-make-loras-with-very-few-images-advice-and-tips-english-and-spanish

训练方法

  1. 在B站上找到一个3D大菲视频，尽可能地截取多个视角的大菲人物（12 ~ 20 张图即可）

  2. 前往 https://www.upscale.media/g/pricing 注册一个账号，为后续批量放大图片做准备（如果你有大会员能看 4K 视频的话应该可以跳过放大这一步）

  3. 前往 https://www.remove.bg/api 获取 api token，用于批量去除图片背景（这个网站每个月有50个免费次数，可以配合第 2. 步的批量放大网站）

  4. 回到第 2. 步的网站，选中上传的图片，点击 Transform 创建 jobs，之后根据自己的需求选择处理方法即可（这里是 upscaler & remove bg）

  5. jobs 可能需要处理大约 5 分钟（取决于你的素材量），之后把处理完的图片压缩包下载到本地即可

  6. （可选）把图片压缩包上传到 https://catbox.moe/ ，之后在 colab 下载下来，这样比直接上传到 colab 速度会快很多

  7. 打开 https://colab.research.google.com/github/Linaqruf/kohya-trainer/blob/main/kohya-LoRA-finetuner.ipynb ，跟着流程走就完事了

  8. 由于本人是懒狗所以全程没配图，感兴趣的话可以自己摸索一下

数据集

https://files.catbox.moe/2fk46x.zip

items.name: Tawnee Stone
items.description:
‼ IMPORTANT ‼

  • Your voice matters! Show your support and leave a post, comment and most importantly a review! ⭐

  • Custom LORAs available upon request. Donations appreciated buymeacoffee.☕

  • (workflow advice below) 👇

📝Biography📝

🌟Tawnee Stone (as requested)🌟

who also goes by Tawnee Xia, but whose real name is Tammy Saris, was born on December 30th, 1982 in Crystal Lake, Illinois, USA. She is of Caucasian ethnicity with brown eyes and brown hair. Tawnee is known for her petite figure, standing at 5'6" (1.68m) and weighing 105 lbs (48 kg). She has a slim waist and curvy hips, with a 32C-26-32 measurement. Tawnee had a navel piercing and was often seen with pigtails in her early work.

Tawnee began her career in the adult entertainment industry in 2001 at the age of 18. She gained popularity for her youthful looks and bubbly attitude. She appeared in over 40-50 videos during her career, performing in various scenes. Tawnee also had her own personal website where she shared exclusive content. She quickly became reknown and was a fan favorite among many.

In her personal life, Tawnee Stone reportedly lived in a small community and did not want to be labelled. However, in the adult industry, she was able to explore herself and fulfil her desires. Tawnee left the industry in 2004, but her legacy lives on as one of the defining stars of her generation. Fans still remember her as the petite woman with a killer body and smile.

It is unclear what Tawnee Stone is doing now, as she has remained out of the public eye since leaving the adult industry. However, her work continues to be enjoyed by fans worldwide, and her official website still remains active. Tawnee's impact on the industry and her popularity among fans cement her status as an icon, and her legacy will continue to be remembered for years to come.

💡Workflow Advice💡

🔧Prompt and Sampling🔧

  • Most images have been generated with LORA weighted @ 1.

  • For photoreal shots, I've found sampling steps ~40 give better results.

  • ControlNet is your friend. Embrace the dark side.😈

    • Tile pre-sample and model is good for extreme close ups

    • I often use segmentation for my generations now

🚀Upscaling🚀

  • Try the Ultimate SD upscale script!

  • Sometimes I just send it to Ultimate SD upscale after a quick render and run 2x at a scale of two.

  • Ultimate SD upscale script used @ ~.15 - .4 denoising using 8x NMKD Faces or 4X UltraSharp redraw upscalers.

🗒️Side Notes🗒️

  • Help me help you: Leave a review if you've used this LORA.

  • Most of my gens are not voodoo or outside of workflows I've indicated here or in my other posts.

    • In other words: Leave a comment if you are having issues getting good output, I'll try to respond with some suggestions.

items.description:
v1.0版本的简介见“About this version”

Introduction of v1.0 version in "About this version"

云墨丹心的触发词为：

Fu Hua(AZ), Chinese clothes,long sleeves,neck collar,belt,boots,hair over one eyes,hair ornament,hairpin,single earring, cloak,

其中的“cloak,“若是显现效果差、或是难以触发，则需要提高模型的权重，或提高”cloak,”自身的权重。

可以加入 “face,“来获得更贴近角色的脸部。

本次lora还训练了云墨的伞，有需要把“Oil-paper umbrella,“将入prompt即可。

 

推荐权重：0.75-0.9

Nsfw推荐权重：0.7-0.8

若脱衣不够干净可以尝试把“Chinese clothes,long sleeves,neck collar,belt,cloak“加入到negative prompt

换装推荐权重：0.6

和上面一样，若原衣服元素仍有残留，同样需要将“Chinese clothes,long sleeves,neck collar,belt,cloak“加入到negative prompt

 

此模型基于“animefull-final-pruned.ckpt”，不同大模型适配程度见图9

 

主要更新内容：

1、换用了更大分辨率的底图，现在的出图的细节效果会比第一版好不少

2、服装的局部可更换度更高，并有了新的内容加入，如披风和伞

3、专门训练了”Face,”来提高脸部的还原度

4、更换了训练的底模，现在在不同大模型下的泛用性会更好一点

 

For the " Azure Empyrea" prompt:

Fu Hua(AZ), Chinese clothes,long sleeves,neck collar,belt,boots,hair over one eyes,hair ornament,hairpin,single earring, cloak,

If the depiction of the cloak appears lackluster or proves challenging to generate, it may be necessary to increase the weight assigned to "cloak," or increase this lora weight.

Optional prompts:Face, Oil-paper umbrella,

 

Recommended weights:

- General: 0.75-0.9

- NSFW: 0.7-0.8

- For outfit changes: 0.6

- If residual elements of the original clothing persist, consider adding "Chinese clothes,long sleeves,neck collar, belt,cloak," in the negative prompt.

 

This model is based on the "animefull-final-pruned.ckpt",and the adaptation degree of different models can be seen in Figure 9.

 

Key updates include:

1. Adoption of higher-resolution base images resulting in significantly improved detail in the generated outputs compared to the initial version.

2. Enhanced capability for partial costume replacement, including the addition of a cloak and umbrella.

3. Specialized training for facial features to enhance facial restoration.

4. Application of a different base model for training, thereby improving the versatility across various base models.

Steps: 100

CFG: 11

Prompt Trigger Words: "<hypernet:gdminthn9k:1> a luxury modern interior design, xxxx room "

Replace the "xxxx" with living room, dining, bath, bed etc.

Tip#1: Try to use the above Steps and CFG settings first and tweak from there. I think 80 steps may be the minimum acceptable quality. CFG 10 is minimum and after 14, will be a hit or a miss. But you can try other settings to fit your needs.
